NATIONAL CONSORTIUM &nbsp;HUMAN RIGHTS TRIENAL CIVSAM 2016-2018 Human rights at the center of the implementation of the Peace Accords. New consortium of three partners: PSD, Coordinaci&oacute;n Colombia Europa Estados Unidos CCEEU and&nbsp; National Movement of victims of state crimes Movice. Administered by Movice (Fundaci&oacute;n comit&eacute; solidaridad presos pol&iacute;ticos FCSPP).
The project's main objective contribute to the realization of human rights in Colombia, with an emphasis on victims' rights and guarantees for the defense of human rights in the context of peacebuilding and strengthening of the rule of law. We made up three national human rights platforms: Somos Defensores Programme, Nal Movement victims of crimes of state and coordination Movice Colombia, United States CCEEU Europe. Administered by: Foundation Solidarity Committee Political Prisoners (stakeholder 321)
&nbsp;This Project under construction with the new definitions copy you in the light of the PE country 2016-2020 Civsam according to the adjustment announced this year 2016 from 27% to the Colombia program. And the sprees of the new model of cooperation to reduce partners.
